    "cooking_instructions": [
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Boil a kettle, then trim the <strong>green stalk[s]</strong> off your<strong> aubergine[s]</strong> and chop into bite-sized pieces</p><p>Add the <strong>chopped aubergine</strong> to a large heat-proof bowl covered with <strong>cling film</strong></p><p>Put the bowl in the <strong>microwave</strong> for 4-5 min or until tender</p><p>Tip: Cooking for 4 or more? Microwave for 6-8 min!</p>",
            "order": 1,
            "image": "/images/instructions/spicy-tuna-and-aubergine-tomato-tortiglioni/step-1.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Chop your <strong>tomato[es] </strong>into wedges</p><p>Peel and finely chop (or grate) your <strong>garlic</strong></p>",
            "order": 2,
            "image": "/images/instructions/spicy-tuna-and-aubergine-tomato-tortiglioni/step-2.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Add your<strong> pasta </strong>to a pot of <strong>boiled water</strong> and bring to the boil over a high heat</p><p>Cook the pasta for 7-9 min (10-12 min for wholewheat) or until cooked with a slight bite</p><p>Once done, drain the pasta, reserving a cup of the <strong>starchy pasta water</strong></p>",
            "order": 3,
            "image": "/images/instructions/spicy-tuna-and-aubergine-tomato-tortiglioni/step-3.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a generous drizzle of <strong>olive oil </strong>over a high heat</p><p>Once hot, add your <strong>microwaved aubergine </strong>and cook for 5 min or until browned</p>",
            "order": 4,
            "image": "/images/instructions/spicy-tuna-and-aubergine-tomato-tortiglioni/step-4.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Once the aubergine has browned, add your <strong>tomato wedges </strong>and <strong>garlic</strong> cook for a further 2 min or until starting to soften</p><p>Once the tomato has started to soften, add your <strong>tomato paste</strong>, <strong>chilli flakes </strong>(can't handle the heat? Go easy!)<strong> </strong>and <strong>balsamic sun-dried tomato paste </strong>with 1 tsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tsp] </span><span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tsp]</span> <strong>sugar</strong></p><p>Cook for 30 secs or until fragrant</p>",
            "order": 5,
            "image": "/images/instructions/spicy-tuna-and-aubergine-tomato-tortiglioni/step-5.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Drain your<strong> tuna</strong></p>",
            "order": 6,
            "image": "/images/instructions/spicy-tuna-and-aubergine-tomato-tortiglioni/step-6.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Once fragrant, add the <strong>drained tuna </strong>and <strong>cooked pasta </strong>to the pan with your <strong>vegetable stock mix </strong>and a splash of the <strong>starchy pasta water</strong></p><p>Season with a generous grind of <strong>black</strong> <strong>pepper </strong>and give everything a good mix up \u2013 this is your <strong>spicy tuna & aubergine tomato tortiglioni</strong></p><p>Chop your<strong> parsley </strong>finely, including the stalks</p>",
            "order": 7,
            "image": "/images/instructions/spicy-tuna-and-aubergine-tomato-tortiglioni/step-7.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>spicy tuna & aubergine tomato tortiglioni</strong></p><p>Garnish with the <strong>chopped parsley</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
            "order": 8
        }
    ],
